<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
  <title>Wryteo — Own Your Words</title>

  <style>
    :root {
      --bg: #0d0f12;
      --fg: #eaeaf0;
      --muted: #9aa0aa;
      --accent: #6cf2c2;
      --card: #151820;
    }

    * {
      box-sizing: border-box;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }

    body {
      font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI",
                   Inter, sans-serif;
      background: var(--bg);
      color: var(--fg);
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .container {
      max-width: 960px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 5rem 1.5rem;
    }

    header {
      margin-bottom: 5rem;
    }

    .badge {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 0.3rem 0.7rem;
      font-size: 0.75rem;
      color: var(--accent);
      border: 1px solid rgba(108, 242, 194, 0.3);
      border-radius: 999px;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }

    h1 {
      font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 6vw, 3.5rem);
      line-height: 1.2;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    }

    p.lead {
      font-size: 1.15rem;
      color: var(--muted);
      max-width: 620px;
    }

    .actions {
      margin-top: 2.5rem;
      display: flex;
      gap: 1rem;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    a.button {
      text-decoration: none;
      padding: 0.75rem 1.2rem;
      border-radius: 8px;
      font-weight: 500;
      transition: all 0.2s ease;
    }

    a.primary {
      background: var(--accent);
      color: #000;
    }

    a.primary:hover {
      opacity: 0.9;
    }

    a.secondary {
      border: 1px solid #2a2f3a;
      color: var(--fg);
    }

    a.secondary:hover {
      background: var(--card);
    }

    section.features {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(240px, 1fr));
      gap: 1.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 5rem;
    }

    .feature {
      background: var(--card);
      padding: 1.5rem;
      border-radius: 12px;
    }

    .feature h3 {
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
      font-size: 1.05rem;
    }

    .feature p {
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 0.95rem;
    }

    footer {
      border-top: 1px solid #1f2430;
      padding-top: 2rem;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 1rem;
    }

    footer a {
      color: var(--muted);
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    footer a:hover {
      color: var(--fg);
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <div class="container">
    <header>
      <span class="badge">Self-hosted · Open-source ready</span>

      <h1>Own your words.<br>Publish on your terms.</h1>

      <p class="lead">
        Wryteo is a lightweight, self-hosted blogging engine for people who think
        by writing. No platform lock-in. No algorithms. Just text.
      </p>

      <div class="actions">
        <a href="#" class="button primary">Get Started</a>
        <a href="#" class="button secondary">View on GitHub</a>
      </div>
    </header>

    <section class="features">
      <div class="feature">
        <h3>Self-hosted by default</h3>
        <p>You run it. Your server, your data, your rules.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="feature">
        <h3>Markdown-first</h3>
        <p>Write in plain text. Version it with Git if you want.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="feature">
        <h3>Minimal & fast</h3>
        <p>No heavy dashboards. No unnecessary features.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="feature">
        <h3>Portable content</h3>
        <p>Your writing is never trapped inside a platform.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <footer>
      <span>© 2026 Wryteo</span>
      <div>
        <a href="#">Docs</a> ·
        <a href="#">GitHub</a> ·
        <a href="#">License</a>
      </div>
    </footer>
  </div>
</body>
</html>

